{"tid":124430,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世界最強的前鋒 伊巴謙莫域霸氣之真相","createTime":"2017-02-17T14:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T10:55:31.000Z","uid":15205,"like":48,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b821d1f77d865c36a3529cb4689335c363e1590f","tid":124430,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>伊巴謙莫域霸氣之真相一覽</strong><br />\n<br />\n「我是來自瑞典馬模地區的一個小地方，那是個貧民窟。但是現在，我在瑞典首都有一座個人雕像。我和其他人感覺不同，我不會被我的出身背景所限制。我相信，我可以統治世界，這是肯定的。」<br />\n<br />\n「我很崇敬簡東拿，我聽了他那些話，不過我想說的很簡單，我來這不想當帝王，而是要做曼徹斯特的上帝！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以上都是伊巴謙莫域親口說的 , 但以下都是一些關於他的傳言</strong><br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域曾經登陸過火星，這就是為什麼那裡沒有生命跡象。<br />\n<br />\n其實伊巴謙莫域20年前就已經死了，只是死神還沒有足夠的勇氣去告訴他。<br />\n<br />\n死神曾經有過一次「瀕-伊巴謙莫域經驗」。<br />\n<br />\n電影「不可能的任務」劇組拒絕伊巴謙莫域去試演，原因很明顯。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域有天遇到驚嘆號，並在它臉上揍了一拳。所以我們現在有了問號。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域從不需要隊友傳球給他，因為皮球害怕他的霸氣而自動過來。<br />\n<br />\n當伊巴謙莫域做伏地挺身的時候，他不是把自己撐起來，他是把地球壓下去。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域是地球上唯一在足球比賽中射破一堵磚牆的男人。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域不需要呼吸，他只是把氧氣當作人質。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域睡覺時會開著小夜燈。不是因為伊巴謙莫域害怕黑暗，而是黑暗害怕伊巴謙莫域。<br />\n<br />\n殘障車位不是專門為了殘疾人士而設的。事實上它是在標明這是伊巴謙莫域的車位，而如果你停在這裡，你會被他打成半殘。<br />\n<br />\n有次伊巴謙莫域在法國渡假,騎腳踏車四處晃晃，最後不小心贏了環法自行車大賽冠軍<br />\n<br />\n害怕蜘蛛稱作恐蛛症; 害怕狹小空間稱作幽閉恐懼症;害怕伊巴謙莫域叫作&quot;邏輯&quot;<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域房間有張棕熊做的地毯; 其實那頭熊還沒死, 牠只是不敢動<br />\n<br />\n曾經有一條伊巴謙莫域路, 但後來改名了; 沒有人可以踏在伊巴謙莫域上頭還活命<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域的日歷3/31之後就是4/2; 沒有人可以愚弄伊巴謙莫域!<br />\n<br />\n有次伊巴謙莫域射了一腳就入了兩球 , 因為他把皮球射到對方守門員的頭上<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域用紙來切剪刀<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域玩過樂高; 這也是金字塔的由來<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域比 YA! 時表示：你還有兩秒鐘才知道皮球已經進網<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域不使用時鐘或手錶，因為現在時間是由他決定的<br />\n<br />\n剛生出來的嬰兒會哭，是因為知道這個世界有伊巴謙莫域在<br />\n<br />\n沒有「進化論」這種東西，只有「伊巴謙莫域允許存活物種清單」而已<br />\n<br />\n絕對不要在 Google 上搜尋伊巴謙莫域，因為你找不到什麼資料，反而還會被他知道你在追蹤他<br />\n<br />\n如果你搜尋伊巴謙莫域，Google 的回應不是「您是不是要查：伊巴謙莫域」<br />\n   而是「在你還有機會時，快逃啊」<br />\n<br />\n妖魔鬼怪們露營時晚上的經典活動：講「伊巴謙莫域故事」<br />\n<br />\n交通警察曾經攔下伊巴謙莫域，那個條子很幸運地只有被警告被放走了<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域曾和超人對打，並賭說輸的人要把內褲穿在褲子外面<br />\n<br />\n光線一直希望自己的速度能有伊巴謙莫域的步速那麼快<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域洗澡不用轉開關，他只是瞪著水龍頭讓它哭而已、洗好時再瞪它水就停了<br />\n<br />\n小孩子都是抱著泰迪熊睡覺，伊巴謙莫域則是大灰熊<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域走進室內時不是開燈，他是「關掉黑暗」<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域出的唯一一次錯：他認為自己犯錯了<br />\n<br />\n當伊巴謙莫域面對鏡子時，鏡子就破碎了：因為鏡子也知道不能夾在兩個伊巴謙莫域之間<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域不玩「躲迷藏」，他玩「躲起來並祈禱我不去找你」<br />\n<br />\n我們在生日時慶祝的不是自己長了一歲，而是伊巴謙莫域又讓你活了一年<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域可以用腳打好鞋帶<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙莫域曾痛扁他的影子，因為老是跟著他又太近，現在影子只敢離他 30 呎遠"},{"pid":"8736f0c850faab3e2f929af551e019e315b667e1","tid":124430,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:06:54.000Z","msg":"伊巴謙莫域從未試過犯越位 , 只是對方守衛被他嚇得不能動"},{"pid":"c37ce148b3c37d90e4c98d1a011109f7feee5fde","tid":124430,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca4ec4aff27a4879e5e2bcf112f14325c83873a","tid":124430,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:12:36.000Z","msg":"憨鳩當有趣"},{"pid":"e7cf96fc45ea9aafef61b2a3cd7acd09cfe91dee","tid":124430,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:14:13.000Z","msg":"羅禮士同伊巴<br />\n邊個勁d"},{"pid":"3bdb75fdffac1a3ecaa43acf5b4d881292af4cc4","tid":124430,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:34:42.000Z","msg":"他知道哭是沒有用的，給我往死裡打。"},{"pid":"36b9599aa7f47e09ea0304509724da87319f642c","tid":124430,"uid":2004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e334d553d5fd31871e0c445b133409a1ecbbc16","tid":124430,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:51:38.000Z","msg":"金正恩黎"},{"pid":"ba646c2ffd92e557329c28223ebcc8ef5d20ec90","tid":124430,"uid":26792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑咩屌你老尾"},{"pid":"0704b12c6c1a58245d8cc029c365f807bb084bca","tid":124430,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾正"},{"pid":"9d39d66fd2f9bef9eb5ec4059a474340ee126231","tid":124430,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"同李小龍打果句呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a828c65dc935d3278ad77f07ba8ad391d9dccb4","tid":124430,"uid":14952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"當伊巴謙莫域做伏地挺身的時候，他不是把自己撐起來，他是把地球壓下去。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7b6198845b441230c5312d6a1c638119262cb7","tid":124430,"uid":7466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ede24b1b47cc9d961a1c52924d9b78a803afbc5","tid":124430,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y54p782.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY54p782.jpg&h=f7962e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/003602_de3b166a6703b619879cac19247ad165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F003602_de3b166a6703b619879cac19247ad165.jpg&h=dcb8a81e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/003603_de3b166a6703b619879cac19247ad165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F003603_de3b166a6703b619879cac19247ad165.jpg&h=34af38bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/003603_6f180755cda5e8cbb47d1a42514b8138.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F003603_6f180755cda5e8cbb47d1a42514b8138.jpg&h=2e462f5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbb1f340ab5de5a8d7d94dacc9c93e10f9ad13bc","tid":124430,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"死啦到底原版係咩"},{"pid":"1c34574e54a3267b8c1602b4912a0e97bf4d51e1","tid":124430,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死啦到底原版係咩</blockquote><br />\n早幾年係高登睇過,唔鬼記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c34017558e93c23ae60082b8379d0f4e6ca04a","tid":124430,"uid":4622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038ec6266efb56737c1c80c9a4bee80b0294cd10","tid":124430,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:50:50.000Z","msg":"原版係咪金正恩"},{"pid":"de868fce7cfe0ea6782f5ef0d059656579999ecf","tid":124430,"uid":18545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>死啦到底原版係咩</blockquote><br />\n早幾年係高登睇過,唔鬼記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCHUCK NORRIS ?"},{"pid":"14640d3c0fa699131b56ffa7bf2faceb2ca6ae66","tid":124430,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"有次伊巴謙莫域射了一腳就入了兩球 , 因為他把皮球射到對方守門員的頭上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7a8cebb9285b967f438ac3d462af9270146403","tid":124430,"uid":14952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:54:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當伊巴謙莫域做伏地挺身的時候，他不是把自己撐起來，他是把地球壓下去。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/005428_fbda4e6d6c8007464d22c4dcd0af13f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F005428_fbda4e6d6c8007464d22c4dcd0af13f3.jpg&h=4ae12a18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f05ea6d55e6f206aaa0a7a184f691d407ad853ef","tid":124430,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"原版chuck norris <br />\n<br />\nChuck Norris can tie his shoes with his feet.<br />\n羅禮士可以用腳打好鞋帶。<br />\n<br />\nChuck Norris' Doesn't wear a Watch, he Decides what Time it is.<br />\n羅禮士不使用時鐘或手錶，因為現在時間是由他決定的。<br />\n<br />\nChuck Norris﻿ doesn't call the wrong number; you answer the wrong phone.<br />\n羅禮士不會打錯電話，而是對方接錯電話。<br />\n<br />\nChuck Norris has a grizzly bear carpet in his room. The bear isn't dead it is just afriad to move.<br />\n羅禮士房間有張棕熊做的地毯：其實那頭熊還沒死，牠只是不敢動。<br />\n<br />\nWhen children go to bed, they take a teddy bear with them. When Chuck Norris goes to bed, he takes a grizzly bear with him.<br />\n小孩子都是抱著泰迪熊睡覺，羅禮士則是大灰熊。<br />\n<br />\nChuck Norris owns a custom belt sander with three settings: Low, High, and Shave.<br />\n羅禮士有一台特製的砂帶研磨機，上面設定是：弱&rarr;強&rarr;刮鬍。<br />\n<br />\nWhen Chuck Norris enters a room, he doesn't turn the lights on, he turns the dark off.<br />\n羅禮士走進室內時不是開燈，他是「關掉黑暗」。<br />\n<br />\nWhen Chuck Norris looks in a mirror the mirror shatters, because not even glass is stupid enough to get in between Chuck Norris and Chuck Norris.<br />\n當羅禮士面對鏡子時，鏡子就破碎了：因為鏡子沒笨到被兩個羅禮士夾在中間。<br />\n<br />\nIn an average living room there are 1,242 objects Chuck Norris could use to kill you, including the room itself.<br />\n一間民宅的客廳裏平均會有 1242 種羅禮士可拿來殺人的物品，包括客廳本身。<br />\n<br />\nChuck Norris always makes the shower head cry.<br />\n羅禮士洗澡不用轉開關，他只是瞪著水龍頭讓它哭而已。<br />\n<br />\nAfter a shower, Chuck Norris dosen't need a towel, he just tells the water to get the hell off!<br />\n洗完澡後羅禮士不需要浴巾擦乾，他只要叫水份離開他的身體就好了。<br />\n<br />\nreference: <a href=\"http://mstar.pixnet.net/blog/post/30158684?utm_content=d010ad69-0a22-4c20-8a42-0611213dcb43&amp;utm_campaign=MAIL_share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmstar.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F30158684%3Futm_content%3Dd010ad69-0a22-4c20-8a42-0611213dcb43%26utm_campaign%3DMAIL_share&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e52be51f\" target=\"_blank\">http://mstar.pixnet.net/blog/post/30158684?utm_content=d010ad69-0a22-4c20-8a42-0611213dcb43&amp;utm_campaign=MAIL_share</a>"},{"pid":"56e325710fac3c7c1f562b14ab85d4bba715e890","tid":124430,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:08:32.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce2166e314e1b929bb8ebae853f67ddeecda581","tid":124430,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\